        <Parent_String>painters by technique, implement, or material employed [300025143], painters (artists) [300025136], artists by medium or work type [300386777], artists (visual artists) [300025103], people in the visual arts [300025101], people in the visual arts and related occupations [300239109], people in the arts [300168455], people in the arts and related occupations [300168331], people in the humanities [300025485], people by occupation [300024980], people (agents) [300024979], People (hierarchy name) [300024978], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
